comments: Morant (MEM) and Thompson (CLE) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Clarkson (CLE) makes marginal contact to Brooks' (MEM) front as he releases from the contact to move into his upward shooting motion.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) makes forearm to ball contact during Clarkson's (CLE) shooting motion, any ensuing contact during the play is deemed incidental.
Valanciunas (MEM) and Thompson (CLE) make incidental foot to foot contact during the rebound.
Sexton (CLE) jumps vertically and maintains a legal vertical position contesting the driving shot attempt by Morant (MEM).
Jackson Jr. (MEM) slides his arm around Thompson's (CLE) waist during the screen but contact does not affect his FOM.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) makes incidental contact to the arm of Love (CLE) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) establishes legal position in Garland's (CLE) path during the pick and absorbs the contact.
Garland (CLE) cleanly dislodges the ball as Jackson Jr. (MEM) attempts to gather the pass, any ensuing contact is deemed incidental.
Crowder (MEM) commits a take foul on Sexton (CLE) .
Jackson Jr. (MEM) establishes legal position in Sexton's (CLE) path during the pick and firms up on his left leg when contact occurs.
As Crowder (MEM) and Sexton (CLE) disengage from the screen, Crowder (MEM) makes incidental contact with Sexton's (CLE) head.
Valanciunas (MEM) makes contact with Love's (CLE) body during the rebound but contact does not affect Love's (CLE) ability to retrieve the ball.
Brooks (MEM) makes contact to  Clarkson's (CLE) off arm during his shooting motion that affects his jump shot attempt.
Crowder (MEM) makes marginal contact with Thompson (CLE) during the screen however Thompson (CLE) is able to move through the contact.
Morant (MEM) commits a take foul on Sexton (CLE).
Jackson Jr. (MEM) does not establish a legal screening position and  extends his arm into Sexton's (CLE) path affecting his ability to defend the shot attempt by Crowder (MEM).
Jackson Jr. (MEM) commits a take foul on Garland (CLE).
